ext-tui-cyan/70 font-medium\">[03] capabilities</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-4xl\">Tech Stack</h2></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-16\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-tui-cyan/40\">01</span><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.04]\"></div><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground/40\">Low-Level &amp; Embedded Systems</span></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-white/[0.03] sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">C++</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</span></div><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">ESP32</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</span></div><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">Arduino</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</span></div><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">RTOS</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-muted-foreground\">◧</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">ADV</span></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-tui-cyan/40\">02</span><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.04]\"></div><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground/40\">Web &amp; Full-Stack Engineering</span></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-white/[0.03] sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">React.js</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</span></div><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">TypeScript</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</span></div><div class=\"group bg-card p-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1a1a1a]\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground/60 transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground\">JavaScript</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-foreground\">■</span></div><span class=\"mt-1 block text-[9px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-wider\">CORE</sp